Package: EBSmoothr
Type: Package
Title: Empirical Bayes Smoothing with L-GP and Matern Priors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "EBSmoothr", "Developers",
      email = "devnull@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: EBSmoothr Developers [aut, cre]
Maintainer: EBSmoothr Developers <devnull@example.com>
Description: Provides empirical Bayes smoothers for Gaussian means using
    local Gaussian-process (L-GP) and Matern spatial priors. Includes a
    TMB-based backend for L-GP and an exact Gaussian INLA/SPDE backend for
    Matern models, returning `ebnm`-compatible posterior summaries.
